{"tid":571891,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得多左好多港女著肉絲","createTime":"2018-02-25T06:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T15:09:22.000Z","uid":82002,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8ee21d8fcb98e7c8e6ebcdaea2f0a24f986253","tid":571891,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:05:10.000Z","msg":"依家香港好多野都跟左大陸啲劣質文化，<br />\n人地根本衣食住行將全包圍。<br />\n以前港女雖然西，<br />\n但起碼打扮化妝衣著無果種庸脂俗粉既味道，<br />\n一睇就知係mk妹，純香港人。<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，港女死剩對腳，<br />\n出街睇下港女對腳，<br />\n都算係作為香港人既一大賞心樂事。<br />\n熱褲仔定短裙，配搭波鞋定高筒鞋，高爭鞋，<br />\n各適其適，鋪陳出一對對既港女淫腳。<br />\n<br />\n其中絲襪，可以話係秋冬兩季既重頭好戲。<br />\n黑絲性感而神秘，<br />\n唔同深淺顏色都可以散發出唔同既吸引力。<br />\n白絲代表住香港人鍾情日系文化既打扮，<br />\n可愛而不失調皮。<br />\n<br />\n肉色絲襪，作為絲襪家族既一道奇葩，<br />\n佢既代言人向來都係大陸阿婆同廣場舞阿嬸。<br />\n但唔知幾時開始，<br />\n落到地鐵站同mk竟然會見到<br />\n港女跟風著左肉絲呢種絲中敗類。<br />\n<br />\n一對劣質既肉絲，色澤不勻，用料差劣<br />\n而且過於肥膩既顏色，<br />\n完全掩蓋左雙腿本來既線條。<br />\n港女想著住肉絲令對腳睇落白啲，<br />\n其實係過猶不及，<br />\n係對自己淫腳既一種褻瀆。<br />\n<br />\n恕我直言，<br />\n當一個港女著左肉色絲襪，<br />\n佢就已經唔再係港女。"},{"pid":"5c8b3c5b79646d484c864dd454f5dee8e1b03735","tid":571891,"uid":45788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:07:13.000Z","msg":"不孝子，你伯母都着緊肉絲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c67d6aa8f2b8d87f7889a4b99a484d7161d9a9","tid":571891,"uid":72415,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7f9e64b907d691fd3aa792199020b9972930fbc","tid":571891,"uid":168414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:13:30.000Z","msg":"有得奶咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a214726a0b7b96909a9b0c01b5cc6b1d4af5e2","tid":571891,"uid":138138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.pcstore.com.tw/~prod/M23764630_big.jpg?P=1502328386\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.pcstore.com.tw%2F~prod%2FM23764630_big.jpg%3FP%3D1502328386&h=0d5cb70e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb87ca29cb511b3cfd85de3b74f9b6cc773a91a9","tid":571891,"uid":68389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:47:17.000Z","msg":"其實係跟韓妹先會著肉絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係人地韓國啲肉絲好隱形  香港果啲係大陸貨先會搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331785a454c8fa027f7834332dc805aff225f67b","tid":571891,"uid":14858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}